| 🔴 Critical | No security headers | Add `helmet` |
| 🔴 Critical | Email data exposed with no auth | Gate with auth middleware |
| 🟡 Medium | No rate limiting | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| 🟡 Medium | Hardcoded port | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| 🟡 Medium | No body size limits | Set `limit` in `express.json()` |
